Summary: Was taking a picture of the moon and another star when I noticed other objects.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was up because Spanky (my dog) was starting to get sick and after he did, I took him outside so he can go to the bathroom. I noticed that the moon was bright and the sky was very clear at that time. I also noticed another bright object to the left of the moon (looking at the pic) and close, so when we went inside I used Droid sky view to see what it was, and I do not remember the name at this time, sorry. I took a picture as close as I could of both the moon and the other object together. It wasn't until 2 days later when I looked at the picture again that I noticed something to the right of the moon (if you are looking at the picture) and another 2 objects below the moon, one of them is a little above the 2 in 2013.
